# MQTT ACL — restrict topic access
# Умная Усадьба Hermes

# Zigbee2MQTT bridge: full access
user zigbee2mqtt
topic readwrite zigbee2mqtt/#
topic readwrite $SYS/#

# Smart Estate backend: read telemetry, send commands
user smartestate
topic read zigbee2mqtt/#
topic write zigbee2mqtt/+/set

# Home Assistant (optional)
user homeassistant
topic readwrite zigbee2mqtt/#
topic readwrite homeassistant/#
